{"tid":796753,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"是誰偷走了摩連奴的時間？","createTime":"2018-08-28T03:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T04:25:04.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9933c9e65463aa2f7bc8310534e99515a777fa","tid":796753,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:49:20.000Z","msg":"英超,頂多都只係1年 <br />\n但係摩連奴過去三年的時間? <br />\n到底去左邊? <br />\n點解大家好似一點印象都無 <br />\n記憶比篡改了?還是時間被盜走了 <br />\n是神偷了?是哥迪奧拿偷了?還是摩連奴自己偷了 <br />\n我通通都不知道,但我只知道,那段時間是摩連奴的寶貴回憶 <br />\n<br />\n一個聯賽盃,一個歐霸盃,一個社區盾,一個英超亞軍<br />\n它們到底去了邊? <br />\n點解大家只把重點收在摩連奴在英超既小小失敗 <br />\n而忘記了它們? <br />\n話摩連奴一成不變,唔該你自己睇下曼聯精華,睇下摩連奴既排陣 <br />\n話摩連奴唔識聽人意見,自己睇下佢用卡域克做助教 <br />\n話摩連奴黑面,自己睇下摩連奴平時接受待人接物,有幾好笑容 <br />\n曼聯好多球員都話摩連奴最好相處 更衣室入邊最無架子 <br />\n<br />\n你估摩連奴教曼聯<br />\n唔想有好似足球小將咁既知心手足 <br />\n唔想有好似ONE PIECE咁既團結志同道合的夥伴 <br />\n無啊,佢只係一個愛德華艾力克 <br />\n手腳受傷了,要獨自背負罪名去尋找勝利 <br />\n<br />\n點解短短一兩個月 <br />\n一向團結既連登會變到分裂 <br />\n大家平時反哥迪奧拿既精神 <br />\n點解會盪然無存? <br />\n大家可以回來嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed9ad17db974022162db7eb8df30f435564cd31","tid":796753,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:50:05.000Z","msg":"無人覆你 我覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb808e3ca754c590697c2568dadc2143a34024f","tid":796753,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"大家可以回來嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4968f22ef1ba24efffcc3856a60a4c30e465b46f","tid":796753,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb808e3ca754c590697c2568dadc2143a34024f","tid":796753,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"大家可以回來嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"叫傑斯教算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"923ec5534b0b7c4c03407c7520449ee4c25c5936","tid":796753,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"打咁大篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}